title: Sheyna
text:
Sheyna () is a <a href="types%20of%20inhabited%20localities%20in%20Russia">rural locality</a> (a <a href="Village%23Russia">village</a>) in <a href="Plesetsky%20District">Plesetsky District</a>, <a href="Arkhangelsk%20Oblast">Arkhangelsk Oblast</a>, Russia. The population was 1 as of 2010. 
Geography.
Sheyna is located 72 km southwest of <a href="Plesetsk">Plesetsk</a> (the district's administrative centre) by road. Kuvakino is the nearest rural locality.
